    <section id="content" role="main" class="rtp-content-section large-8 medium-6 small-12 columns rtp-multiple-post" >
        
            <h1 class="post-title rtp-main-title">Tags: <span>Chris Hedges</span></h1>
        <article id="post-10196" class="post-10196 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-news-items tag-chris-hedges tag-fort-lee tag-george-washington-bridge-scandal tag-libertarianism tag-neocon clearfix rtp-post-box">
            
            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/01/14/jon-stewart-on-chris-christie-absolutely-hilarious/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Jon Stewart on Chris Christie&#8230;Absolutely Hilarious">Jon Stewart on Chris Christie&#8230;Absolutely Hilarious</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2014-01-14T14:36:35+00:00">Tuesday Jan 14, 2014</time> at 2:36 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/01/14/jon-stewart-on-chris-christie-absolutely-hilarious/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Jon Stewart on Chris Christie&#8230;Absolutely Hilarious">Leave a comment</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>Regular readers know that I am no fan of Chris Christie. Just yesterday, I <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/01/13/the-trouble-with-chris-christie-by-chris-hedges/">highlighted a post written by Chris Hedges</a> on the New Jersey Governor, which is a must read expose if you haven&#8217;t already.</p>
<p>While Hedges&#8217; criticisms of Christie are nothing to laugh about, Jon Stewart&#8217;s certainly are. Have fun with this hilarious clip!</p>
<span class='embed-youtube' style='text-align:center; display: block;'><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='620' height='379' src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/cnOQlhjdH3s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' frameborder='0'></iframe></span>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div style=display:inline-block;>
<div style=float:left;margin-right:6px;>
